{#**
 * 角色提示词基础模板
 * 格式参考: video-prompt-templates.md v2.0
 * 使用方式: jinja2 render with character data
 *#}
{% block HEADER %}
35mm film photography, high ISO, grain texture, authentic RAW photo,
character turnaround sheet for cinematic period film, four separate full body shots on a single white canvas,
{% endblock %}

{% block SUBJECT %}
subject: a real {{ age }}-year-old East Asian {{ gender }} actor, {{ height }} height, {{ build }}, realistic human anatomy with {{ anatomy }}, {{ skin }},
{% endblock %}

{% block FACE %}
facial features: {{ hair }}, {{ eyes }} irises with {{ gaze }}, {{ expression }}, {{ special }},
{% endblock %}

{% block ATTIRE %}
attire: {{ attire }}, {{ attire_details }},
{% endblock %}

{% block VIEWS %}
views (from left to right):
1. strict front view, {{ view_front }},
2. 3/4 front view facing {{ view_34 }},
3. strict profile view facing {{ view_profile }},
4. full back view showing {{ view_back }},
{% endblock %}

{% block TECHNICAL %}
technical details: shot on ARRI Alexa, {{ lens }}mm lens, f/{{ aperture }}, sharp focus on {{ focus }}, {{ lighting }},
{% endblock %}

{% block BACKGROUND %}
background: pure seamless white paper backdrop, absolute blank background, zero digital artifacts, totally clean background
{% endblock %}

{% block NEGATIVE %}
negative: {{ negative_prompt }}
{% endblock %}
